Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:06.86,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,欸… 欸…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.55,0:00:06.86,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,来 来 来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.53,0:00:07.86,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:09.37,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,阿尔法大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:13.85,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,希妲制作了鳗当劳的新口味汉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.85,0:00:16.02,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,我知道 所以来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.02,0:00:19.47,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,阿尔法大人真的很喜欢鳗当劳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.47,0:00:22.53,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,是呢 他也很喜欢这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:24.56,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,但是这个实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.56,0:00:27.34,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,实在太革新了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.34,0:00:28.56,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.56,0:00:33.25,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,至今希妲开发出的新产品都很成功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.25,0:00:36.52,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,无论是夹入炭烧黄瓜的汉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:39.41,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,还是奶油炸肉饼汉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:43.58,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,其创新及全新的美味 都获得了高销量和广泛好评
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:44.21,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,Ｖ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.21,0:00:45.66,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,但是这次…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.66,0:00:48.18,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,这次说实话真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.18,0:00:49.57,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,希妲 说明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:53.33,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,将汉堡的概念 颠覆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.33,0:00:54.43,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,概念？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.43,0:00:58.34,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,将主料用面包包裹这点对调
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.34,0:00:59.31,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.31,0:01:02.01,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,用鲔鱼替换面包
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.01,0:01:02.82,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:05.92,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,不是包裹主食 而是用主食来包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:07.56,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.56,0:01:09.08,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,阿尔法大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:11.95,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,汉堡因为使用面包
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.95,0:01:14.12,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,所以卡路里一定会很高
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:16.01,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,如果要发展女性顾客的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:18.98,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,使用主料的汉堡我觉得也挺有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.98,0:01:21.69,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,确实有道理… 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:25.64,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,那么希妲 里面夹的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:27.92,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,夹的是… 米饭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.92,0:01:30.53,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,不错啊 感觉很配
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:34.03,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,但是米饭很烫的话会传到主料 需要降低温度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:36.84,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,考虑到保存方法 加上醋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:38.85,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,酱料打算用什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.85,0:01:41.39,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,和风 酱油最佳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.39,0:01:45.93,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,嗯 还缺最后的点睛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:47.01,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,山葵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.01,0:01:50.25,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,完美 然后就是取名了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:52.19,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,简单的比较好
